{"tid":1430511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解咁撚大鑊都冇人理","createTime":"2019-08-07T18:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:36:14.000Z","uid":302098,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cdfe5ba462f0a087e65ab6881aa0ed4d67e3301a","tid":1430511,"uid":302098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:16:27.000Z","msg":"我係P牌，呢個係我第一個post。<br />\n特登入嚟係因為有樣大鑊嘢大家一直冇留意，但影響好大<br />\n就係原來<strong>99Van嘅其中一個老闆，就係元朗恐襲打香港人嘅黑幫大佬個仔</strong>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1epJgO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1epJgO.gif&h=b21d0dd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n蘋果早幾個月已經寫過：<br />\n<em>港聞專題：小桃園飯局猛人 入區會參與規劃 　元朗「田雞東」掃棕地等賠償</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190307/20627838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F20627838&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=9d94070b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F20627838&h=236fd931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190307/20627838</a><br />\n不過因為冇將呢件事發大嚟寫，所以冇人理<br />\n<br />\n99van係由三條友聯合創辦，當中包括鄧ｘ威 Nixk Tang（最左邊嗰個先係）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgudBHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgudBHv.jpg&h=79ee038b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/headlinehk/photos/pcb.1600527009997209/1600526809997229/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheadlinehk%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.1600527009997209%2F1600526809997229%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=dd4b9655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/headlinehk/photos/pcb.1600527009997209/1600526809997229/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n而鄧ｘ威就係田ｘ東個仔！（中間嗰個）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxhF1dG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxhF1dG.jpg&h=6b4046ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>壹週刊：田雞東專訪我唔係江湖大佬</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GTEYzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GTEYzc&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=86b45da8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GTEYzc</a><br />\n當時壹仔直頭去埋婚宴直擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F99EPjpqnqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF99EPjpqnqw&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=b1fcbfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F99EPjpqnqw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40TqsUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40TqsUh.jpg&h=c6d9ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（原link 仲search到但已fail）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家唔好資助元朗國恐怖分子！</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔識田ｘ東係邊個？<br />\n睇下舊文。<br />\n<em>元朗反黑拘299人　小桃園飯局座上客 囝囝田雞東被捕</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170809/20116252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170809%2F20116252&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=99338ad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170809%2F20116252&h=4ba6dcd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170809/20116252</a>"},{"pid":"faaf161e2028d26f476cc695628a924ded915ea4","tid":1430511,"uid":186276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48bedf99e4cd65e78629d7b5bfc5e62a6cddd090","tid":1430511,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor